flowRoot.flowPara: Minimal scroll indicator should be faded in as soon as a list gets scrolled and faded out as soon as scrolling stops.
Basic scroll indicator should be faded in as soon as a list gets scrolled and faded out as soon as scrolling stops.
As soon as the scroll bar gets touched, it gets extended to advanced scroll indicator.

As soon as advanced scroll indicator is activated, the list should jump to nearest list category and use it's text label. Advanced indicator is the positioned over the category. Moving finger up and down jumps between categories. For an example on behavior, have a look on how it works on Meego Harmattan. I can provide a video if needed.
